data.name: smoothFrameLabel.ToolTip
data.value:
Works like a framerate limiter. The value should be the refreshrate of your screen.
Can not be lower than 25. Entering lower values or empty spaces will reset the setting to the default value (60).

data.name: physxLabel.ToolTip
data.value: Demanding feature! Uses CPU for PhysX instructions (because this machine doesn't use a NVIDIA graphics card) - EXTREMELY demanding. Breakable tiles, realistic paper simulation, advanced smoke effects.
